graph LR
    ODHController[ODH Notebook Controller]

    %% External Dependencies (Required)
    ODHController -->|watches CRs| KubeflowController[Kubeflow Notebook Controller<br/>v0.0.0-20220728153354]
    ODHController -->|creates ingress| OpenshiftRoute[OpenShift Route API<br/>route.openshift.io/v1]
    ODHController -->|injects sidecar| OAuthProxy[OpenShift OAuth Proxy<br/>ose-oauth-proxy:latest]
    ODHController -->|provisions certs| ServiceCA[OpenShift Service CA]
    ODHController -->|framework| ControllerRuntime[controller-runtime<br/>v0.11.0]
    ODHController -->|core APIs| K8s[Kubernetes API<br/>v1.24.2+]

    %% External Dependencies (Optional)
    ODHController -.->|optional proxy| ClusterProxy[OpenShift Config API<br/>config.openshift.io/v1]

    %% Internal ODH Dependencies
    Dashboard[ODH Dashboard] -->|consumes Routes| ODHController
    OpenshiftIngress[OpenShift Ingress] -->|processes Routes| ODHController
    ServiceCAOp[Service CA Operator] -->|provisions TLS| ODHController

    %% Runtime Dependencies (created resources interact with)
    NotebookPod[Notebook Pod<br/>with OAuth Proxy]
    ODHController -->|creates/manages| NotebookPod

    NotebookPod -->|authenticates| OAuthServer[OpenShift OAuth Server]
    NotebookPod -->|authorizes| K8sAPISAR[Kubernetes API<br/>SubjectAccessReview]
    NotebookPod -.->|optional egress| ProxyService[Cluster-wide Proxy]

    Router[OpenShift Router] -->|routes traffic| NotebookPod

    %% Upstream dependency
    KubeflowController -->|creates StatefulSets| NotebookPod

    %% Styling
    style ODHController fill:#4a90e2,stroke:#333,stroke-width:4px,color:#fff

    %% External dependencies
    style KubeflowController fill:#999,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px,color:#fff
    style OpenshiftRoute fill:#999,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px,color:#fff
    style OAuthProxy fill:#999,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px,color:#fff
    style ServiceCA fill:#999,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px,color:#fff
    style ControllerRuntime fill:#999,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px,color:#fff
    style K8s fill:#999,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px,color:#fff
    style ClusterProxy fill:#999,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px,color:#fff,stroke-dasharray: 5 5

    %% Internal ODH dependencies
    style Dashboard fill:#7ed321,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style OpenshiftIngress fill:#7ed321,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style ServiceCAOp fill:#7ed321,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px

